item.title: Question about gates/doors
item.dc:creator: @frostscapeserver frostscapeserver
item.description:
@frostscapeserver wrote:

You must have the wrong coordinates. Click the door in-game. Then look at the server command prompt and get the coordinates and object id from there.
Go into client.java (server sided)
Search for

deletethatobject

At the bottom of a list of delethatobjects
Add

deletethatobject(xxxx, yyyy);
